Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.13,0:00:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,STORM-SHIFT. Polycrisis readiness for USMC installations.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.13,0:00:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The polycrisis era is here — storms cascade into supply, inventory,\Nand fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.13,0:00:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Operator picks installation, storm scenario, optional co-event.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Five datasets: NASA Earthdata, FIRMS, NFIP, FEMA Climate-SC, CA\NLogistics.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.14,0:00:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Six projection agents fan out in parallel — flood, supply, inventory,\Nconsumption, impact, fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.15,0:00:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sankey diagram renders the cascade chain — storm to flood to supply to\Ninventory red.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.15,0:00:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,72-hour cascade timeline · polycrisis multiplier surfaces non-linear\Ncompounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kamiwaza-deployed model writes the Polycrisis Readiness Brief.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.16,0:00:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Storm models stay in your enclave. No cloud egress. Set\NKAMIWAZA_BASE_URL.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,0:01:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Built on the Kamiwaza Stack. Deploy in hours, not months.
